2013年5月，佛蒙特州立法通过安乐死，成为美国第4个安乐死合法化的州。<ref>[http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/20/nation/la-na-nn-vermont-governor-signs-death-with-dignity-measure-20130520 Vermont governor signs 'death with dignity' measure] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/20/nation/la-na-nn-vermont-governor-signs-death-with-dignity-measure-20130520 |date=20130709024503 }}Los Angeles Times</ref>
